      "role": "user",
      "content": "well if the doses have to be high, what kind of amount are we talking about? like if i bought concentrate supplements or some kind of high potency garlic oil, how much do people usually take to see a real effect? i just want to know if it's even possible to get a good result naturally so i can decide if it's worth trying.",
